Super jazzed about my gifts from @goodsvintage One of my favorite places to shop in Philadelphia. Be sure to pop in and check ‘em out. 🌻🌷🦓💍🪴💫🪄💜

A lil bit about Goods Vintage:

Goods Vintage has been operating for just over 8 years under owner and curator Keith Allibone. We are a vintage jewelry and antiques store located in the heart of South Philadelphia’s Italian Market. We offer hand-picked rare jewelry, distinct home decor, and other eclectic treasures at a neighborly price. We’re operated by a small energetic staff who love meeting and connecting with locals and tourists.

CDMX 🇲🇽 Primera semana

I started taking Spanish classes a year ago. It’s one of the main reasons I wanted to come to Mexico City - to immerse myself in the culture. What a gift it has been. Viva la Vida. 💛🇲🇽
Algunas fotos de la semana 2.
Estatuas de la Ciudad de México

CDMX: Semana tres 
A friend said to me that Mexico City is paradise and that’s spot on. 🎯 From the people to the food to the cafes that stay open until 9pm to the culture. Todo. Que ciudad! Gracias por tres maravillosos semanas. Voy a volver. 💛💚

For now - the sentiment of…I love going, but I also love coming home feels so right.
